== Notes ==
* [[Pole position]]: [[Mario Andretti]] - 1:16.39
* Fastest Lap: [[Mario Andretti]] - 1:20.06
* Lap Leaders: [[James Hunt]] 5 laps (1-5); [[Mario Andretti]] 70 laps (6-75).

